      "audioFile": "necro_match_start_necro_astro_convo02_02",
      "audioUrl": "audio/necro_match_start_necro_astro_convo02_02.mp3",
      "text": "A condesending cop.  Shocking.",
      "duration": 2.596
    },
    {
      "order": 3,
      "character": "Holliday",
      "audioFile": "astro_match_start_necro_astro_convo02_03",
      "audioUrl": "audio/astro_match_start_necro_astro_convo02_03.mp3",
      "text": "Snark isn't gonna keep you alive.",
      "duration": 2.222
    },
    {
      "order": 4,
      "character": "Graves",
      "audioFile": "necro_match_start_necro_astro_convo02_04",
      "audioUrl": "audio/necro_match_start_necro_astro_convo02_04.mp3",
      "text": "What, and you are?",
      "duration": 1.18
    },
    {
      "order": 5,
      "character": "Holliday",
      "audioFile": "astro_match_start_necro_astro_convo02_05",
      "audioUrl": "audio/astro_match_start_necro_astro_convo02_05.mp3",
      "text": "Against my better judgement.",
      "duration": 1.727
    },
    {
      "order": 6,
      "character": "Graves",
      "audioFile": "necro_match_start_necro_astro_convo02_06",
      "audioUrl": "audio/necro_match_start_necro_astro_convo02_06.mp3",
      "text": "You're quite the civil servant",
      "duration": 1.992
